{% comment %}
  Hotjar tracking loader. Emits the merchant's Hotjar embed code verbatim —
  the full <script> snippet copied from Hotjar's install page (works for both
  the legacy static.hotjar.com bootstrap and the newer Contentsquare-platform
  t.contentsquare.net tag, and survives future tag-format changes without a
  theme edit). The code is a per-shop secret (aico://secrets/…) set by the
  shop admin — trusted input, deliberately output unescaped. Gated on the
  tracking flag + a non-empty snippet, so environments without the secret
  (local/preview) never load Hotjar. Rendered once from layout/theme.liquid
  so it covers every page.
{% endcomment %}
{% if settings.aico_hotjar_enabled and settings.aico_hotjar_embed_code and settings.aico_hotjar_embed_code != '' %}
  {{ settings.aico_hotjar_embed_code }}
{% endif %}
